 BTS柾国宣布首次个人演唱会“Golden Live On Stage” https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-first-solo-concert-golden-live-on-stage-3511342?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bts-jungkook-first-solo-concert-金色现场舞台Rhian DalyMon, 09 Oct 2023 02:05:51 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3511342 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="BTS 柾国" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该节目将在他的首张个人专辑（也名为“Golden”）发行后举行</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-first-solo-concert-golden-live-on-stage-3511342">防弹少年团柾国宣布首次个人演唱会后，“Golden Live On Stage”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="BTS 柾国" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bts">防弹少年团</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungkook">柾国</a>公布了他的首场个人演唱会“Golden Live On Stage”的详细信息。</p><p>该节目将在歌手即将推出的首张个人专辑（也称为“Golden”）发行后的几周内举行。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/bts-jungkook-seven-review-solo-era-uk-garage-3468564">在《七》中，防弹少年团的柾国在英国车库的夏日高潮中开启了他的个人生涯</a></strong></li></ul><p>柾国将在首尔奖忠体育馆担任主角，音乐会将通过网络向世界各地的歌迷直播。该活动将于 11 月 20 日晚上 8 点（韩国标准时间）（格林威治标准时间上午 11 点）举行，门票面向持有 ARMY 会员或从 Weverse 商店购买“Golden”的粉丝。</p><p> <a href="https://weverse.io/bts/notice/15597" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Weverse 上的一则通知写道：</a> “柾国‘Golden’现场演唱会将表演专辑中的多首歌曲。” “我们热切期待您对这位艺术家的独特展示带来的喜爱和支持。” </p><figure id="attachment_3511359" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3511359" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3511359" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-2023.jpg" alt="BTS 柾国" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bts-jungkook-3d-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3511359" class="wp-caption-text"> BTS 的 Jungkook 图片来源：BIGHIT MUSIC</figcaption></figure><p>虽然柾国之前曾进行过独奏表演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bts-jungkook-and-latto-perform-seven-at-global-citizen-2023-3503319">包括最近在纽约举行的全球公民音乐节</a>，但“Golden Live On Stage”将标志着他作为独唱艺术家的首场大型音乐会。有关票务和直播的更多详细信息将在未来几周内公布。<br />柾国将于 11 月 3 日发行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-star-jungkook-announces-debut-solo-album-golden-3508584">他的首张个人专辑《Golden》。</a>这张专辑将收录 11 首歌曲，包括最近与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/latto">Latto</a>合作的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-solo-single-seven-3463264">《Seven》</a> ，以及这位明星与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-harlow">Jack Harlow</a>合作的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jungkook-jack-harlow-single-3d-3503479">《3D》</a> 。</p><p>凭借《3D》，柾国成为第一位在英国单曲打入前五名的韩国独唱艺人。他的最新专辑排名第五，而《七》则最高排名第三。</p><p>与此同时，这位歌手最近在一次聆听派对上 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-grateful-for-haters-internet-trolls-3507618">谈到了对他的仇恨者的感激之情</a>。在 Stationhead 上举办在线活动宣传“3D”时，这位 BTS 成员引用了一位粉丝的评论，称他们“正在研究[支持]其他偶像团体”。</p><p>他回答说，评论者“可以自由地这样做”，但他“感谢那些支持我的人”。随后，柾国补充道，他也“对恶意评论表示感谢”。 “这意味着他们把时间花在我身上。我认为这是某种兴趣。正确的？他们是不同类型的粉丝，”他说。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-first-solo-concert-golden-live-on-stage-3511342">防弹少年团柾国宣布首次个人演唱会后，“Golden Live On Stage”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
